comments.content: This forum is for General Discussions only; type id requests are not to be posted here. Please post your request at: [http://typophile.com/typeid](http://web.archive.org/web/20130901044349/http:/typophile.com/typeid "http://typophile.com/typeid")
Furthermore, there is no reason to suspect that it is an existing typeface: it is two simple forms, repeated and rotated.
